---
layout: base.njk
title: Често задавани въпроси
description: Отговори на въпроси за микроблейдинг, ламиниране, грижа след процедура и записване на час при Brows and lashes ValyaMatovska.
permalink: /faq/
pageI18nKey: faq
---

{% set f = home.faq if home and home.faq else {} %}
{% set items = f.items if f.items else [] %}

<main id="main">
  <section
    class="mb-section section-padding bg-white/70 scroll-mt-20"
    aria-labelledby="faq-page-heading"
  >
    <div class="container-custom">
      <header class="mb-header mx-auto mb-8 text-center md:mb-10">
        <span class="mb-eyebrow justify-center" data-i18n="home.faq.eyebrow">{{ f.eyebrow | default("Въпроси и отговори") }}</span>
        <h1 id="faq-page-heading" class="mb-title mt-2 text-center" data-i18n="home.faq.title">
          {{ f.title | default("Често задавани въпроси") }}
        </h1>
        {% if f.pageLead %}
        <p class="site-lead mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted" data-i18n="home.faq.pageLead">
          {{ f.pageLead }}
        </p>
        {% endif %}
      </header>

      {% if items and items.length %}
      {% set faqItems = items %}
      {% set faqAccordionName = "faq-page" %}
      {% include "faq-accordion.njk" %}
      {% else %}
      <p class="text-center text-muted" data-i18n="ui.comingSoonFaq">Скоро ще добавим отговори на често задавани въпроси.</p>
      {% endif %}

      <p class="faq-page__back">
        <a href="{{ '/' | url }}#contact" class="faq-page__back-link" data-i18n="ui.faqBackContact">Контакти и записване</a>
        <span class="site-footer__sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <a href="{{ '/' | url }}" class="faq-page__back-link" data-i18n="ui.faqBackHome">Начална страница</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

{% include "faq-accordion-script.njk" %}
